---
title: Seared Halloumi & Broccoli Salad with Parmesan & Dijon Mustard
description: Juicy seared halloumi takes centre stage in this fresh and zesty dish! Paired with a crisp broccoli salad, punchy Dijon mustard, and a sprinkle of Parmesan, it’s a perfect balance of bold flavours and bright, cheesy goodness.

